Package: rd4
Title: R Bindings for Reading and Querying Dense Depth Data Dump (D4) Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Pamela", "Russell", , "pamela.russell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
    person("Seth", "Stadick", , "sstadick@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: rd4 provides R bindings for reading and querying Dense Depth Data 
    Dump (D4) files. The D4 format provides fast analysis and compact storage of 
    quantitative genomics datasets. For full details, see Hou et al. Nature 
    Computational Science 2021 (https://doi.org/10.1038/s43588-021-00085-0).
